snippet: The Iranian-American photojournalist, a woman with dual citizenship, was detained last month along with a reporter for The Washington Post and his wife.
abstract: Iranian-American photojournalist who was detained in July on the same day as Washington Post reporter Jason Rezaian and his wife Yeganeh Salehi is released; relatives refuse to reveal her identity.
lead_paragraph: The Iranian-American photojournalist, a woman with dual citizenship, was detained last month along with a reporter for The Washington Post and his wife.
